plot1<-plot_model(model=gam_cog_lrg, type = "pred",terms = c("age"), colors = "gray41", ci.lvl=.475,line.size = 2) +
  geom_jitter(data = data, aes(x = age, y =within.Cog_ToM ),alpha = 0.3,position = "jitter", color ="ivory3" ) +
  geom_line(color = "#AEC3A8", size = 2)+
  theme_light()+
  labs(
    title = " ",
    x = "Age",
    y = "Cognitive ToM",
    colour = "Gears"
  )+
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0.05, .3))+
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = seq(5, 17, by = 2))+
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(size = 12, face = "bold"))+
  theme(axis.text.y = element_text(size = 12, face = "bold"))
